    <id>http://www.zlu.me/blog/2012/03/13/nginx-tricks</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Test configuration change without restarting Nginx</p>

<p>nginx -t (sudo)</p>

<p>restarting working process</p>

<p>kill -HUP <code>cat /var/run/nginx.pid</code> (replace nginx.pid with your system)</p>

<p>log file full</p>

<p>cat /dev/null | sudo tee /var/log/nginx/error.log</p>

<p>then reopen log file</p>

<p>kill -USR1</p>
]]></content>
